snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! City seal UEFA Champions League ticket after victory at Fulham | Fulham 0-2 Man City
snippet.description:
Goals from Ilkay Gundogan and Erling Haaland fired City to a 2-0 win at Fulham in our final Premier League game of the season to seal the Club’s place in next season’s UEFA Champions League.

The victory ensured Pep Guardiola’s side finished in third place in the Premier League – and just as significantly booked our ticket into next term’s elite European competition.

Gundogan opened the scoring at Craven Cottage with a spectacular 21st minute overhead kick with what the German’s first league goal since re-joining the Club last summer.

City largely dominated affairs in west London and the three points were then confirmed on 72 minutes when Haaland converted from the penalty spot after Gundogan had been brought down.

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

snippet.title: MENGGILA DI MEDAN #01
snippet.description:
Holla~!
Apa kalian baik-baik aja di ujung sana~?

--------------------------------------------------------------

Danau Toba.
Tempat aku gak liburan dan kerja.
Tapi anehnya, ternyata hati aku bisa istirahat di antara kebisingan itu~🥹

Gak ada itinerary mewah.
Gak ada outfit kece.
((Soalnya aku selalu kece dengan outfit sederhana sekali pun. Kalian langsung keluar dari kolom deskripsi.))
😂🤣😂

Cuma ada pertemuan antara aku, danau, langit, suara ombak dan suara hati.

Terlepas dari seberapa bising kehidupan kita.
Seberapa banyak deadline yang numpuk — seperti cucian yang gak ada habisnya.
Seberapa berat tekanan dan tuntutan dari kanan-kiri.

Kadang yang kita butuhin hanya menyendiri untuk beberapa jam.
Untuk ngobrol sama diri sendiri.
Untuk nge-check keadaan jiwa dan batin kita.

Sejauh ini, alam salah satu dopamin aku yang paling ampuh.
Termasuk melihat langit dari jendela kamar — di saat manusia terlelap dan hanya menyisakan aku, langit, dan...
kawanan alienku~👽🛸


Semoga kalian juga bisa menemukan dopamin sederhana.
Bukan untuk terlihat keren.
Bukan untuk sekedar "soulfully aesthetic".
Tapi untuk kita tetap waras.
Untuk kita tetap tenang.

💛💛💛


xoxo,

RSW

snippet.title: Rapercoyo - LAVORA (Official Music Video) Trilogi Eps 1 || Sakjane aku ngerti kowe main neng mburi
snippet.description:
#LAVORA #Rapercoyo #OfficialMusicVideo
TRILOGI LAVORA 2025
Kali ini Spesial Anniversary Lavora ke 5 Tahun kami akan merilis Trilogi atau 3 cerita berkelanjutan yang dikemas dalam bentuk Single & Short Movie. Beberapa judul lagu yang akan kami rilis yaitu Rapercoyo (Episode 1), Asing (Episode 2), Rasah Bali 2 (Episode 3), dan Short Movie by Lavora sebagai penutup. Terimakasih sudah mensupport band Lavora hingga berumur 5 tahun ini. Semoga beberapa single yang akan kami rilis di tahun 2025 ini bisa menemani patah hati kalian dan semoga kita bisa berkembang bersama.

snippet.title: Infinix GT 30 Pro Nih Bosss! Kuat Banget 4 Jutaan!
snippet.description:
Infinix GT 30 Pro akhirnya resmi rilis di Indonesia, dan ini dia HP gaming paling ambisius dari Infinix tahun ini! Pakai chipset MediaTek Dimensity 8350 Ultimate (4nm) yang powerful, baterai 5500mAh awet, dan layar AMOLED 144Hz super mulus, ditambah fitur gaming canggih seperti GT Trigger, AI FPS Booster, sampai wireless charging, semua ada di sini! Tapi apa itu cukup buat saya terkesima? Cek videonya sampai habis ya!
 
Spesifikasi Infinix GT 30 Pro:
• Jaringan 2G/3G/4G/5G
• Berat: 192gram
• Dual SIM (Nano), tanpa slot MicroSD
• Layar AMOLED 6.78” 1080 x 2436 pixels, 144Hz refresh rate, HBM hingga 1600 nits
• OS Android 15, XOS15
• MediaTek Dimensity 8350 Ultimate (4 nm)
• GPU Mali G615 MC6
• 256GB/8GB RAM, 512GB/12GB RAM
• Kamera belakang:
50MP AI Main Camera
• Pro Mode + AR Effect
• Kamera depan: 13MP
• WiFi 6, Bluetooth 5.4, NFC, USB-C, Dual SIM
• Fingerprint di layar (optical)
• Baterai Li-Po 5500mAh
• 45W Wired Charging
• Wireless Charging + Reverse Wireless Charging
• Fitur Gaming: GT Trigger (shoulder trigger fisik), GT MagCharge Cooling System + GT MagCase (versi bundle), AI Gaming System (FPS Booster, Thermal & Battery Management)
• Desain Cyber Mecha Body dengan RGB Mechanical Light Wave
• Warna: Dark Flare, Shadow Ash, Blade White
